description: React component for user profile management in the Burning Man camp logistics app, allowing users to view and edit their personal details, accommodation, crew, and dates.

methods.name: Profile()
methods.description: React functional component that renders a user profile form with fields for name, email, accommodation, crew, experience, arrival, and departure dates. Uses React hooks for state management and context for user authentication.

methods.name: onSave
methods.description: Handles form submission by updating the user context with the current profile data and showing a placeholder alert.
